217s         by version number.
217s     
217s         >>> names = 'bar', 'foo', 'Python-2.7.10.egg', 'Python-2.7.2.egg'
217s         >>> _by_version_descending(names)
217s         ['Python-2.7.10.egg', 'Python-2.7.2.egg', 'bar', 'foo']
