218s         def set_extraction_path(self, path):
218s             """Set the base path where resources will be extracted to, if needed.
218s     
218s             If you do not call this routine before any extractions take place, the
218s             path defaults to the return value of ``get_default_cache()``.  (Which
218s             is based on the ``PYTHON_EGG_CACHE`` environment variable, with various
218s             platform-specific fallbacks.  See that routine's documentation for more
