218s         def get_cache_path(self, archive_name, names=()):
218s             """Return absolute location in cache for `archive_name` and `names`
218s     
218s             The parent directory of the resulting path will be created if it does
218s             not already exist.  `archive_name` should be the base filename of the
218s             enclosing egg (which may not be the name of the enclosing zipfile!),
218s             including its ".egg" extension.  `names`, if provided, should be a
218s             sequence of path name parts "under" the egg's extraction location.
